{
  "id": "7523782745248632094",
  "text": "Day 1: Challenging myself to share one herb a day and some notes from my Materia Medica collection as an offering to the collective community 🪴🤗🩵 Today we’re learning about: Shatavari (Aspargus Resimosa) apart of the Lilyaceae family this is truly one of my favorite herbs to lean on in time of need. She’s best in as a milk tea though personally I’ve used the powder in my pancake mix with Maca to jump start my day. Yes.. lol Shatavari is an aphrodisiac herb 😏 and works great with others in that category. 🌿It also works as a mild laxative and diuretic so be advised when working with her. 🩵 Let me know your thoughts and questions in the comments. If you had additional information feel free to leave those too we’re building a community here. We learn together 🩵 #shatavari #herbs #herbalism #herbalist #blackherbalist #landstewardship #spiritualtiktok ",
