  "id": "7578463749183491360",
  "text": "This is Shatavari — a powerful Ayurvedic herb for women.\nMix a small spoon of Shatavari powder and half a spoon of sugar into warm milk and drink daily.\nIt supports hormone balance, improves egg quality, boosts fertility, helps regulate periods, and promotes healthier skin.\nShare this with women who might benefit from this incredible herb.\nWrite the word sova and get my Ayurvedic Hormone Balance Guide.\n#shatavari #ayurvedicherbs #hormonebalance #womenshealth #naturalremedies #ayurvedalifestyle",
