{
  "id": "7481280505141382442",
  "text": "We’ve all been there, feeling tired, moody, or struggling with weight, and thinking it’s just part of being a woman.\nBut these common symptoms could actually be signs of hormonal imbalance.\nHere’s what to watch for:\n1. Fatigue or low energy\n2. Irregular or painful periods\n3. Mood swings or anxiety\n4. Difficulty losing weight\nIf these sound familiar, this is your body sending clear signals, and it’s crucial for you to listen, and with the right approach, you can actually regulate your hormones.\n#hormonalhealth #PCOSsupport #balanceyourhormones #healthyhormones",
