  "id": "7592699854749519126",
  "text": "⚠️ Intermittent fasting doesn’t land the same on female bodies as it does on male ones — especially if you’re young, training, stressed, and menstruating 🩷\n\nWhen food is delayed, women’s hormones and stress systems respond differently, which can impact mood, recovery, metabolism and our fertility hormones.\n\nThis isn’t about me being anti-fasting. Instead, I just want to give you the full picture about the science we have right now for effects of intermittent fasting on female bodies, so you can make informed choices about YOUR body. \n\nYou’ve got this. OK love you byeeee xoxo \n\n#WomensHealth #IntermittentFasting #HormoneHealth #nutritionist #health",
