{
  "id": "7493641898486238506",
  "text": "Protein and fiber all day… Bowls like this is how I balanced my hormones and keep them balanced 💕\n\nDetails\nFor the Rice\n- 1 cup rice\n- 2 cups water\n- 2 tsp coconut oil\n- Sea salt, to taste\nFor the Carrot Salad\n- 2 carrots, ribboned or shaved\n- A splash of apple cider vinegar\n- A splash of olive oil\n- Sea salt, to taste\nFor the Ground Beef\n- 1 pack ground beef\n- ½ pack Siete seasoning\n\nInstructions\n1. In a pot, combine rice, water, coconut oil, and a pinch of sea salt. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat, cover, and simmer until the rice is tender and water is absorbed.\n2. In a bowl, toss the ribboned carrots with apple cider vinegar, olive oil, and sea salt. Set aside to marinate while everything else cooks.\n3. In a skillet over medium heat, cook the ground beef until browned. Add Siete seasoning and stir well to combine. Cook until fully done and flavors meld.\n4. Assemble your bowl and enjoy!\n\n#healthyrecipe #Easyrecipe #Holisticrecipe #Foodasmr #wellnesstips #hormonehealth ",
