  "id": "7610075155242437908",
  "text": "dinner deets ⬇️\n\nquantity AND quality are so important for period recovery + hormone health!! when I seriously dialled in on the nutrients my body needed for a regular, healthy cycle, that’s when it started coming like clockwork. no more guessing when my next cycle was going to be.\n\n🥩 steak - heme iron + b12 to support progesterone + energy when you’re naturally a little lower in the luteal phase\n\n🍠 japanese + purple sweet potatoes - slow carbs to support blood sugar + cortisol balance (purple = extra antioxidants for inflammation)\n\n🥕 carrots - beta carotene to support hormone production + liver detox pathways\n\n🥬 sautéed spinach - magnesium + potassium to help with cramps, bloating, + nervous system support\n\n#periodrecovery #harecovery #antiinflammatory #wholefoods #hormonehealth ",
