{
  "id": "7593397442305985814",
  "text": "POV: you want something quick and healthy for your WFH lunch…\n\nThis anti-inflammatory plate took 10 minutes and is loaded with foods that help calm inflammation, support hormones, and keep you full (aka no 3pm crash).\n\nHere’s what’s on it:\n🥑 Smashed avocado — healthy fats for hormone balance + glowing skin\n🐟 Smoked salmon - omega-3s to fight inflammation and support your brain\n🍳 Fried egg - protein + choline for energy and blood sugar balance\n🍞 Sourdough toast - easier to digest and less blood-sugar spiking\n🫐 Blueberries - antioxidants that help reduce inflammation and support your gut\n\nThis is the kind of “soft life” lunch that still loves your body back 🤍\nEasy, nourishing, and something you can actually stick to!!#endometriosis #antiinflammatory #lunch #hormonehealth #womenshealth \n\nSave this for your next “what do I eat?” moment ✨",
