  "id": "7608615929194253581",
  "text": "Polycystic Ovary Syndrome (PCOS): Why Hormones Go Haywire\nPCOS is the leading cause of female infertility, affecting up to 12% of women of reproductive age. This 3D Pixar-style animation breaks down the hormonal imbalance that creates ovarian cysts, disrupts ovulation, and causes symptoms like irregular periods, acne, and excess hair growth. Discover what happens inside your body and why lifestyle changes matter.\n\n#PCOS #PolycysticOvarySyndrome #WomensHealth #HormonalImbalance #PCOSAwareness #HealthAnimation #Infertility #ReproductiveHealth #PeriodProblems #InsulinResistance #MedicalAnimation #WomensWellness #HormoneHealth #PCOSDiet #EndocrineSystem #PixarStyle #3DAnimation#FYP #viral",
