  "id": "7576024611180039431",
  "text": "Are you struggling with low libido? I think This Is such an important conversation that many of us are afraid to have with medical professionals or loved ones, so let’s chat today about what might be driving this. \n\nFor many of the driving factors, except being on birth control, this is where my clinic can help. \n\nMy clinic Nourishing Apothecary is available online to people in Australia. I have an amazing team of naturopaths, and for this I would recommend Mel or Toni. I would start with a free discovery call with either of them, have a chat and go from there. You can find out more and book through my website www.nourishingapothecary.com \n\n#libido #lowlibido #naturopath ",
