{
  "id": "7603867156224265503",
  "text": "🗣️ Let’s talk Libido! 👀\nTestosterone is not the only hormone that affects desire—and pushing it higher and higher won’t magically fix everything.\n\nLow libido is complex: hormones, neurotransmitters, stress, sleep, meds, relationship dynamics, metabolic health… ALL matter.\n\nIf your provider’s only solution is ‘let’s just increase your testosterone,’ you deserve a better plan.\n✨ There are options. ✨”\n#libido #testosterone #hormonehealth #womenshealth #nursepractitioner @Beauty Boss Co. ",
